          "settings": {
            "question": "Are these safe if my toddler puts them in their mouth?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. These wax crayons are made with a non-toxic, taste-safe formula. While they are not food, they will not harm your child if chewed or licked — which toddlers commonly do during play.</p>"
