        "faq_2": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Will the wax wash off furniture and walls?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. The wax formula wipes clean from most hard surfaces (tables, tiles, walls) with a damp cloth. For fabrics, pre-treat with warm water and soap before a standard wash cycle.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_3": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What age are these suitable for?",
            "answer": "<p>Recommended for ages 2 and above. The chunky grip design is specifically sized for toddler hands, making them the ideal first crayons for young children.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_4": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do these compare to markers and pencils?",
            "answer": "<p>Wax crayons offer a different texture experience — smoother, softer marks that are great for broad colouring. Pair them with markers (for bold lines) and pencils (for detail) to give your child a complete art toolkit.</p>"
          }
